<p>
  <span class="nym">Virgil</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>Vergilius, Virgilius</i>, a Roman clan name of unknown meaning.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 1st C BC Roman poet.</p>
</div>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>Renewed popularity of the poet during the Renaissnance contributed to the use of the name in Italy in the 16th C.  <i>Vergilius</i> or <i>Virgilius</i> was also sometimes used to Latinize the Irish name <a class="nym" href="Fergal">Fergal</a>.</p>
</div>
  


<dl>
<dt><span class="area">Italy</span></dt>
<dd>
<dl>
<dt><span class="lang">Latin</span></dt>
